sequenceDiagram
    participant Cand as Candidate
    participant API as AIBF API
    participant ATS as ATS engine
    participant BE as Bias engine
    participant HR as HR reviewer

    Cand->>API: POST /api/resumes
    API->>ATS: evaluate(features, job)
    ATS-->>API: score, verdict, data_points
    API->>BE: analyze(features)
    BE-->>API: bias_score, flagged, explanations
    API-->>Cand: ats_decision + flag
    opt flagged
        HR->>API: GET /api/admin/flagged
        HR->>API: POST /api/admin/feedback (accept/override)
        HR->>API: POST /api/model-training/retrain
        API->>BE: retrain(feedback)
        BE-->>API: new model_version + threshold
    end
